@startuml DailyDataEntry
actor Workers
actor Cashier
participant DailyUI
participant Database

Note over Workers,Database: MORNING: Attendance Tracking

Workers->>Cashier: Arrive at farm, show QR code
Cashier->>DailyUI: Scan QR codes (entry)
DailyUI->>Database: Save attendance records

Note over Workers,Database: AFTERNOON: Health Reports

Workers->>Cashier: Veterinary paper report:<br/>(House 1: 4920 chickens, 3 dead, 22째C)<br/>(House 2: 3000 chickens, 1 dead, 23째C)<br/>(House 3: 2800 chickens, 2 dead, 21째C)<br/>(House 4: 6500 chickens, 5 dead, 22째C)

Cashier->>DailyUI: Enter health data for all houses
DailyUI->>DailyUI: Calculate mortality rates
DailyUI->>Database: Save health records

alt Mortality > 5%
    DailyUI->>Database: Create ALERT: High mortality
end

Note over Workers,Database: AFTERNOON: Egg Collection

Workers->>Cashier: Report: 4200 eggs, 150 cracked
Cashier->>DailyUI: Enter egg data
DailyUI->>Database: Update inventory (+4050 clean eggs)<br/>Save production record
DailyUI->>DailyUI: Compare with yesterday

alt Production drop > 20%
    DailyUI->>Database: Create ALERT: Production drop
end

Note over Workers,Database: AFTERNOON: Feed & Supplies

Workers->>Cashier: Report: 100 kg feed used, 450 kg left
Cashier->>DailyUI: Enter feed consumption
DailyUI->>Database: Update inventory (-100 kg feed)
DailyUI->>DailyUI: Calculate days remaining (450/100 = 4.5 days)

alt Stock < 7 days
    DailyUI->>Database: Create ALERT: Low feed stock
end

Note over Workers,Database: EVENING: Exit Tracking

Workers->>Cashier: Leave, show QR code
Cashier->>DailyUI: Scan QR codes (exit)
DailyUI->>Database: Update attendance (calculate hours)
@enduml